<section class="section section--off-white" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header">
      <h2>Custom Roofing Quote in 3 Simple Steps</h2>
      <p>From first call to finished roof in three simple steps</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 1.5H8.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 3.75v16.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 20.25V3.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H13.5m-3 0V3h3V1.5m-3 0h3m-3 18.75h3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>1: Get in Touch</h3>
          <p>Call us or fill in the form. We'll have a quick chat about what you need and book a free inspection at a time that works for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.35 3.836c-.065.21-.1.433-.1.664 0 .414.336.75.75.75h4.5a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75 2.25 2.25 0 0 0-.1-.664m-5.8 0A2.251 2.251 0 0 1 13.5 2.25H15c1.012 0 1.867.668 2.15 1.586m-5.8 0c-.376.023-.75.05-1.124.08C9.095 4.01 8.25 4.973 8.25 6.108V8.25m8.9-4.414c.376.023.75.05 1.124.08 1.131.094 1.976 1.057 1.976 2.192V16.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 18.75h-2.25m-7.5-10.5H4.875c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h9.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V18.75m-7.5-10.5h6.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.375m-8.25-3 1.5 1.5 3-3.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>2: Free Inspection and Quote</h3>
          <p>We'll visit your property, assess the roof, and give you an honest, written quote with no hidden costs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m2.25 12 8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>3: Work Completed to Standard</h3>
          <p>We carry out the work on schedule, leave the site clean, and back everything with our 15-year warranty.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
